1 AN ACT relating to authorizing the payment of certain claims against the state
2 which have been duly audited and approved according to law and have not been paid
3 because of the lapsing or insufficiency of former appropriations against which the claims
4 were chargeable or the lack of an appropriate procurement document in place, making an
5 appropriation therefor, and declaring an emergency.
